Decision criteria suggestions:
  - Higher RECALL on should-match = better at finding related concepts
  - Lower FPR on should-not-match = fewer spurious matches
  - Higher PURITY = topics have semantic coherence
  - Lower Top10% = no mega-cluster problem
  - Reasonable median size = useful granularity (not all size-1, not all huge)
